{"data":[{"date":"15:51 02/08","title":"HLV Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb t\u00e2n binh Alisson","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/hlv-klopp-tiet-lo-nhung-dieu-dac-biet-tu-tan-binh-alisson.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alisson, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea3 Mignolet v\u00e0 Karius nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Mignolet ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00ec Karius l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e2m l\u00fd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/HLV-Jurgen-Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Alisson-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alisson l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady HLV Klopp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf\u00a0ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson </span>c\u1ee7a Roma. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra t\u1edbi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Alisson ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Alisson, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp phat bieu ve tan binh Alisson\" title=\"HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/hlv-klopp-tiet-lo-nhung-dieu-dac-biet-tu-tan-binh-alisson.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Liverpool, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Alisson. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi BL\u0110 chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0a Alisson v\u1ec1 Anfield. T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u1edf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, Alisson r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang gi\u1edd. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra c\u1ea7u ti\u1ebfn. Alisson th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng minh, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cAlisson cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ngay c\u1ea3 trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, ngay c\u1ea3 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1917","checkdouble":"192554"},{"date":"16:17 02/08","title":"Tottenham s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/tottenham-sap-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-tri-gia-30-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Lewis Cook c\u1ee7a Bournemouth \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Spurs \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 20 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham d\u1ef1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, Tottenham l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng duy nh\u1ea5t ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0o.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Lewis Cook v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Lewis Cook v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Tottenham-muon-mua-Lewis-Cook-voi-gia-30-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Pochettino v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, vi\u1ec7c Spurs kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo The Sun, Tottenham s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Spurs kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh khi\u1ebfn NHM c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1edfi khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi HLV Mauricio Pochettino mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Daniel Levy chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 Tottenham mua th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t im \u1eafng, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt NHM \u0111ang lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a \u201cG\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\u201d \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Lewis Cook</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Lewis Cook c\u1ee7a Bournemouth \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Spurs \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham chi 30 trieu bang mua Lewis Cook\" title=\"Tottenham chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Lewis Cook\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/tottenham-sap-co-tan-binh-dau-tien-tri-gia-30-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Lewis Cook</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Lewis Cook l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Bournemouth. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 ra s\u00e2n 29 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London nh\u1eafm Lewis Cook nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Dembele. Vi\u1ec7c Victor Wanyama v\u00e0 Harry Winks d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f2n Eric Dier v\u00e0 Moussa Dembele ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau World Cup 2018 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Spurs \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBournemouth b\u1ecf ra 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Lewis Cook, l\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Bournemouth c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1916","checkdouble":"192555"},{"date":"16:08 02/08","title":"Koscielny ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1eddi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/9/koscielny-tiet-lo-thoi-diem-roi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Rudiger ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a HLV Emery trong hi\u1ec7p hai \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Arsenal l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Lacazette ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Chelsea c\u1ea7n Emerson h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c Chelsea 1-1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c Chelsea 1-1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Diem-nhan-sau-tran-chien-can-suc-Chelsea-1-1-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Emerson h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Sarri h\u01a1n Alonso</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap h\u1ecd x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u0169ng n\u1ea3y sinh khi Marcos Alonso kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 Emerson Palmieri \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil khi anh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlonso l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal \u0111\u1eb7t ra m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn cho Sarri v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Alonso khi m\u00e0 Bellerin v\u00e0 Mkhitaryan li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh Chelsea.</div>\r\n<h2>Guendouzi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng l\u1edbn\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matteo Guendouzi\" title=\"Matteo Guendouzi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/170354-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Matteo Guendouzi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Matteo Guendouzi l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arsenal, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Emery trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ee7 90 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGuendouzi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u1ea3m tr\u00e1ch v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u00f9i s\u00e2u. Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 l\u01a1 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGuendouzi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Arsenal \u0111\u00eam qua. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ecdc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 sang t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Guendouzi l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn chung, sao tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Premier League. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Lorient c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e2ng cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n s\u1ed1ng s\u00f3t qua nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Premier League.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-chien-thang-cua-arsenal-truoc-chelsea-172-192524.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1i nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Petr Cech ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cech\" title=\"Cech\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/170417-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Cech c\u1ea3n c\u00fa penalty quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap Arsenal chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi S\u00e9c \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. Anh c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Alvaro Morata ghi b\u00e0n n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho Chelsea tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty \u1edf ph\u00fat 15. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Cech c\u0169ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa s\u00fat penalty c\u1ee7a Loftus-Cheek \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u1edb h\u00eanh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng 36 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 m\u1ea5t tinh th\u1ea7n m\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Cech c\u0169ng mang l\u1ea1i cho Arsenal nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111ong \u0111\u1ebfm khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 Cech l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<h2>Morata l\u1ea1i \u0111em c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cho Sarri\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/170506-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Morata b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Morata \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 HLV Sarri c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft HLV Sarri r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111em ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia l\u00e3o luy\u1ec7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd c\u0169ng mong mu\u1ed1n h\u1ed3i sinh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Morata.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, Morata li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Cech tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t 11m v\u00e0 c\u0169ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ec7 trong nh\u1eefng pha \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 Morata th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 Inter tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y Chelsea kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m b\u00e0n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n th\u00ec Sarri kh\u00f3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i Chelsea l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 1-1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/2/Arsenal-vs-Chelsea_mp4_Output_1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1915","checkdouble":"192556"},{"date":"16:05 02/08","title":"3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/3-thuong-vu-chuyen-nhuong-co-the-duoc-mu-hoan-thanh-ngay-trong-tuan-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U \u0111ang l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong th\u1eddi gian qua. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u HLV Mourinho s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y?</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 10 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa, TTCN c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i Anh s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda. Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi n\u0103m, theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c L\u0110B\u0110 Anh ban h\u00e0nh, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/2019 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 9/8 (gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng), tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u 1 tu\u1ea7n, thay v\u00ec k\u00e9o d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 31/8 nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm t\u1eadp trung ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho CLB. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c TTCN \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda s\u1edbm, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ra nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Man United trong vi\u1ec7c tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u00e9p gi\u00e1.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi M.U l\u00fac n\u00e0y, sau c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng g\u1ed3m Fred, Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 Lee Grant, HLV Jose Mourinho v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1ebd thanh l\u00fd g\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 'ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba' trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y. V\u1eady \u0111\u00e2u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y?</p>\r\n<h2>3. Matteo Darmian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/3-thuong-vu-chuyen-nhuong-MU-co-the-hoan-tat-trong-tuan-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u1edf c\u1ea3 Anh v\u00e0 Italia \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Matteo Darmian s\u1ebd chia tay M.U ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 17 tr\u1eadn, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 8 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Premier League.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng, Matteo Darmian c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i v\u00e0 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t CLB nh\u01b0 Juventus, Inter v\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111\u1ec1u b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Inter \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Sime Vrsaljko, Juve c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Joao Cancelo c\u00f2n AC Milan c\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao M.U. T\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng Darmian s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford th\u00eam 6 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y CLB Napoli \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00eca tay ra v\u1edbi anh. V\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<h2>2. Marcos Rojo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Marcos Rojo\" title=\"trung ve Marcos Rojo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/everton-duoc-khuyen-tranh-xa-marcos-rojo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a MU \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Chris Smalling, Phil Jones, Eric Bailly hay Victor Lindelof, Marcos Rojo \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i gia nh\u1eadp Manchester United t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2014 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 16 tri\u1ec7u B\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 100 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf\" v\u00e0 t\u1eebng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i UEFA Europa League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u00eam \u1ea3 khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n 12 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Marcos Rojo \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng song \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c HLV Mourinho gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c b\u00e1o c\u00e1o g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y cho th\u1ea5y Everton \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i. Theo \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh n\u1ebfu chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<h2>1. Toby Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alderweireld\" title=\"Alderweireld\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/Chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-he-2018-Kho-quen-roi,-suong-khong-chiu-duoc!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Toby Alderweireld, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. T\u1eeb l\u00e2u HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c Eric Bailly. V\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u01b0a th\u00edch c\u1ee7a anh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo tin t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, l\u00fac n\u00e0y HLV Mourinho \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd t\u1edbi hai ng\u00f4i sao Maguire v\u00e0 Alderweireld. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Leicester \u0111ang 'h\u00e9t gi\u00e1' r\u1ea5t cao cho Maguire, Alderweireld \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u1ea1i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1eabn kinh nghi\u1ec7m nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i con s\u1ed1 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Darmian v\u00e0 Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 mua Alderweireld, tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-0208-172-192540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-0208.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-0208-172-192540.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 02/08</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 02/08.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca-172-192523.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/11/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tu-bo-maguire-va-alderweireld-mu-muon-mua-mina-cua-barca-172-192523.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Bom t\u1ea5n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018</span><br>\r\nMU mua Yerry Mina l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/kovacic-khong-den-mu-vi-mourinho-184-192497.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/2/kovacic-khong-den-mu-vi-mourinho.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/kovacic-khong-den-mu-vi-mourinho-184-192497.html\">Sao Real t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho</span><br>\r\nTheo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Mateo Kovacic quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gia nh\u1eadp Man United v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i do Mourinho x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1914","checkdouble":"192557"},{"date":"17:24 02/08","title":"B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, M.U s\u1ebd t\u1ed1ng kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cc\u1ee7a n\u1ee3\u201d Martial","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/mu-muon-doi-martial-lay-lewandowski-cua-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng HLV Jose Mourinho song g\u1eb7p tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c \u1edf v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayern mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Martial</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Anthony Martial trong v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng qua. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Allianz Arena h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong khi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Man United \u0111\u00f2i 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea3 Martial th\u00ec Bayern ch\u1ec9 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n M.U c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ch\u00ecm xu\u1ed3ng qu\u00e1 nhanh. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Martial sau nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i g\u00e2y ra. Trong 2 m\u00f9a d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jose Mourinho, c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Monaco kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/MU-muon-doi-Martial-lay-Lewandowski-cua-Bayern-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Martial khi\u1ebfn HLV\u00a0Mourinho r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. Martial v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o ra b\u00ea b\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u00fang h\u1ea1n sau khi r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o s\u1ef1 ra \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi con th\u1ee9 2. HLV Mourinho r\u1ea5t b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f3i v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t 2 tu\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea3u Martial t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ecbt m\u1edd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Mourinho t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau th\u00edch t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski. Nh\u00e2n ti\u1ec7n c\u00f3 Bayern \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, M.U mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Ph\u00eda Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u00e1c th\u00eam m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ba Lan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Niem hy vong so mot cua DT Ba Lan, Robert Lewandowski im tieng trong tran dau nay.\" title=\"Ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ba Lan, Robert Lewandowski im ti\u1ebfng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/lewandowski-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-ba-lan-truoc-senegal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>M.U mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Martial l\u1ea5y Lewandowski</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Bayern, nh\u1eefng Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi Martial. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, M.U kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 tin M.U ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00ean t\u1edbi 500 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n Lewandowski \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia nh\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Bayern tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Lewy, song h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n Martial thay th\u1ebf l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Franck Ribery \u0111\u00e3 35 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/3-thuong-vu-chuyen-nhuong-co-the-duoc-mu-hoan-thanh-ngay-trong-tuan-nay-187-192557.html\">3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/mourinho-muon-mu-chieu-mo-bo-doi-cua-real-187-192515.html\">Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dai-gia-italia-chua-buong-tha-matteo-darmian-172-192507.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i gia Italia ch\u01b0a bu\u00f4ng tha Matteo Darmian</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-bi-mat-dam-phan-chieu-mo-pogba-180-192489.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/btc-icc-to-ra-thong-cam-voi-mourinho-ve-luc-luong-172-192359.html\">BTC ICC t\u1ecf ra th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Mourinho v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1913","checkdouble":"192561"},{"date":"17:07 02/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/diem-nhan-sau-tran-chien-can-suc-giua-chelsea-va-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Rudiger ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a HLV Emery trong hi\u1ec7p hai \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Arsenal l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Lacazette ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Chelsea c\u1ea7n Emerson h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c Chelsea 1-1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn c\u00e2n s\u1ee9c Chelsea 1-1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Diem-nhan-sau-tran-chien-can-suc-Chelsea-1-1-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Emerson h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Sarri h\u01a1n Alonso</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap h\u1ecd x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u0169ng n\u1ea3y sinh khi Marcos Alonso kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 Emerson Palmieri \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil khi anh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlonso l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal \u0111\u1eb7t ra m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn cho Sarri v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Alonso khi m\u00e0 Bellerin v\u00e0 Mkhitaryan li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh Chelsea.</div>\r\n<h2>Guendouzi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng l\u1edbn\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matteo Guendouzi\" title=\"Matteo Guendouzi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/170354-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Matteo Guendouzi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Matteo Guendouzi l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arsenal, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Emery trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ee7 90 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGuendouzi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u1ea3m tr\u00e1ch v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u00f9i s\u00e2u. Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 l\u01a1 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGuendouzi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Arsenal \u0111\u00eam qua. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ecdc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 sang t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Guendouzi l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn chung, sao tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Premier League. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Lorient c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e2ng cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n s\u1ed1ng s\u00f3t qua nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Premier League.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-chien-thang-cua-arsenal-truoc-chelsea-172-192524.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1i nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Petr Cech ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cech\" title=\"Cech\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/170417-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Cech c\u1ea3n c\u00fa penalty quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap Arsenal chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi S\u00e9c \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. Anh c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Alvaro Morata ghi b\u00e0n n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho Chelsea tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty \u1edf ph\u00fat 15. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Cech c\u0169ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa s\u00fat penalty c\u1ee7a Loftus-Cheek \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u1edb h\u00eanh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng 36 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 m\u1ea5t tinh th\u1ea7n m\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Cech c\u0169ng mang l\u1ea1i cho Arsenal nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111ong \u0111\u1ebfm khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 Cech l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<h2>Morata l\u1ea1i \u0111em c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cho Sarri\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/170506-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Morata b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Morata \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 HLV Sarri c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft HLV Sarri r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111em ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia l\u00e3o luy\u1ec7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd c\u0169ng mong mu\u1ed1n h\u1ed3i sinh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Morata.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, Morata li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Cech tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t 11m v\u00e0 c\u0169ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ec7 trong nh\u1eefng pha \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 Morata th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 Inter tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y Chelsea kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m b\u00e0n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n th\u00ec Sarri kh\u00f3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i Chelsea l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 1-1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/2/Arsenal-vs-Chelsea_mp4_Output_1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1912","checkdouble":"192562"},{"date":"17:21 02/08","title":"M\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a Real Madrid: Sau \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/mua-he-am-dam-cua-real-madrid-sau-dinh-cao-la-vuc-sau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh ch\u00e2n nh\u01b0 v\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n thay th\u1ebf si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-rua-mat-cua-mu-truoc-real-184-192465.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Manchester United</span> tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi \u1edf Real Madrid. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a, v\u1eady n\u00ean c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn g\u00ec th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1ng cho c\u1ea3 k\u1ebb th\u1eafng l\u1eabn ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng c\u1ea3 t\u00e1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0110TQG, thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u00f9ng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu m\u00e0i \u0111\u0169ng qu\u1ea7n tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m Sau \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m Sau \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/4-ly-do-tin-rang-los-blancos-se-sup-do-o-mua-giai-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 v\u1eabn t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 th\u00edch th\u00fa khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u00e2n binh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil Vinicius Junior s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Karim Benzema tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Lopetegui cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ra m\u1eaft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u00ednh mi\u1ec7ng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u1ea3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha gh\u00e9t n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: <em>\u201cN\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi t\u00f4i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac r\u1ed3i.\u201d</em> \u2013 Vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Bernabeu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eebng n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf CR7, \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u1edd m\u1edd hi\u1ec3n hi\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a Real Madrid Sau \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"M\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a Real Madrid Sau \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Mua-he-am-dam-cua-Real-Madrid-Sau-dinh-cao-la-vuc-sau-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Vinicius \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung cho h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Lopetegui khi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 Bale v\u00e0 Benzema qua nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. Ho\u1eb7c \u00f4ng \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf Bernabeu trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ho\u1eb7c \u00f4ng \u0111ang v\u1ee5ng v\u1ec1 tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn v\u00e0 ki\u1ec1m h\u00e3m k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng bom t\u1ea5n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u00dd \u0111\u1ed3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 l\u00e0 g\u00ec, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00e1c Madridista kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, vui v\u1ebb g\u00ec d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ch\u00fat \u00edt n\u1ebfu t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ed1t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh c\u00e1i quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngay t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/juventus-chieu-mo-cristiano-ronaldo-co-nhung-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-176-191505.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd ra \u0111i v\u00e0 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus</span>, \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n g\u1ea7n xa \u0111\u00e3 \u00fap m\u1edf cho nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 mang t\u00ean Neymar, Kylian Mbappe, Eden Hazard hay Harry Kane, hay \u00edt nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u201cch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y\u201d \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng Robert Lewandowski hay Edinson Cavani. T\u1edbi gi\u1edd n\u00e0y, ch\u1eb3ng ai trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u1ea1c quan s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/4-ly-do-tin-rang-los-blancos-se-sup-do-o-mua-giai-toi-180-192418.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/4-ly-do-tin-rang-los-blancos-se-sup-do-o-mua-giai-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/4-ly-do-tin-rang-los-blancos-se-sup-do-o-mua-giai-toi-180-192418.html\">4 l\u00fd do tin r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos s\u1ebd s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t \u1edf th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao v\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do Real Madrid s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec thay \u0111\u1ed5i, hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1ebd suy y\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean h\u1ecd \u1edf La Liga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean. Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Clement Lenglet, Arthur Melo v\u00e0 Malcom, trong khi Atletico Madrid \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng Rodri, Thomas Lemar v\u00e0 Gelson Martins.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Real Madrid th\u00ec sao? H\u1ecd c\u00f3 Vinicius nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tu\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f4i m\u01b0\u01a1i, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c dung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, quy ho\u1ea1ch cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Alvaro Odriozola c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i v\u1edbi Dani Carvajal v\u00e0 Nacho nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Ronaldo ngay t\u1eeb v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ngay c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Bale hay Benzema c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e0ng ho\u00e0ng c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb1ng kh\u00e1c c\u01a1 m\u00e0. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m vung ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129, Real Madrid tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf chi ti\u00eau \u00edt h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Barca v\u00e0 Atletico trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale Benzema\" title=\"Bale Benzema\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/171113-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f2n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Bale v\u00e0 Benzema</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, CLB ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i m\u1edbi kh\u00f3 tin \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 Zidane, gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 Los Blancos ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafc kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb m\u00e3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ef1 tr\u1ecb tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh cao th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Madridistas v\u1eabn s\u1ebd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng khoan dung v\u1edbi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 ba La Liga n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng con c\u01b0ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u00e1ch th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i trong ba n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho vinh quang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c h\u1ebft. M\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e2u c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 43 b\u00e0n/38 tr\u1eadn xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u0103ng quang ba chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap b\u1ea1c li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu trong v\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Real Madrid \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u1ecfi m\u01a1 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn t\u1eeb trong n\u01b0\u1edbc ra ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi \u00c2u, k\u00e9o theo thi\u1ec7n ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V kh\u00f3 t\u00ednh v\u00e0 tai qu\u00e1i b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 r\u1ed3i s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng ti\u00eau tan. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng hay l\u00e0 ch\u1ebft, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd, Florentino Perez!<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2><strong>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid h\u00e8 2018:</strong><strong><br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-201819-khoi-nguyen-cho-zidane-va-pavon-thuc-su-180-192419.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/real-madrid-201819-khoi-nguyen-cho-zidane-va-pavon-thuc-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-201819-khoi-nguyen-cho-zidane-va-pavon-thuc-su-180-192419.html\">Real Madrid 2018-19: Kh\u1edfi nguy\u00ean cho Zidane v\u00e0 Pavon th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1</span><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, r\u1ed3i Zinedine Zidane nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean. Real Madrid li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho c\u00e1i g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Galaticos?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong-180-191983.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong-180-191983.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: Hazard s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n, nh\u01b0ng thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo? Kh\u00f4ng!</span><br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n cung 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/m\u00f9a khi Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Juventus, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1911","checkdouble":"192564"},{"date":"17:44 02/08","title":"L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c r\u00fat \u0110T Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/18/ldbd-iraq-phu-nhan-viec-rut-dt-olympic-iraq-khoi-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, t\u1edd Reuters cho r\u1eb1ng L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c r\u00fat \u0110T Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi ASIAD\u00a0</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a, sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i U16 Iraq b\u1ecb ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n gian l\u1eadn tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin L\u0110B\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c r\u00fat \u0110T Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c r\u00fat \u0110T Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/18/ldbd-iraq-phu-nhan-viec-rut-dt-olympic-iraq-khoi-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n\u00a0\u0110T Olympic Iraq r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi ASIAD 2018 nh\u01b0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e3ng Reuters th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng BTC ASIAD 18 s\u1ebd m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam b\u1edfi c\u01a1 c\u1ea5u c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i do b\u1ea3ng C ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang 3 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110\u00f4ng Timor v\u00e0 Syria, trong khi b\u1ea3ng A v\u00e0 E c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 5 \u0111\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, Reuters, h\u00e3ng th\u00f4ng t\u1ea5n uy t\u00edn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u1eabn ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb L\u0110B\u0110 Iraq cho bi\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd r\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic Iraq kh\u1ecfi \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft: \"Iraq v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U23 t\u1edbi Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng suy \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 r\u00fat lui. M\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb IFA ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i U23 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Ngu\u1ed3n tin n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Iraq \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD, sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Erbil \u1edf ph\u00eda b\u1eafc Iraq\".\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Iraq t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110\u00f4ng Timor v\u00e0 Syria. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb \u0110\u00f4ng Timor th\u00ec hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Iraq.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam-168-192552.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-palestine-noi-gi-ve-olympic-viet-nam-168-192552.html\">HLV Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nV\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng U23 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 s\u00e1ng 2/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\">HLV Uzbekistan \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1910","checkdouble":"192566"},{"date":"17:36 02/08","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-gonzalo-higuain-toi-ac-milan.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn San Siro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Leonardo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Massimiliano Mirabelli, sau \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u h\u1ecd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Leonardo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan Ai vui ai bu\u1ed3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan Ai vui ai bu\u1ed3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Gonzalo-Higuain-toi-AC-Milan-Ai-vui-ai-buon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leonardo l\u1eadp chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Leonardo l\u00e0m Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Paolo Scaroni c\u1ee7a AC Milan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;Leonardo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1&nbsp;l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 2018&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1eb1m t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, Leonardo \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. AC Milan \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Higuain t\u1eeb Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung phong t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 31 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a AC Milan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 42 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, AC Milan ch\u1ec9 ghi c\u00f3 56 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. H\u1ecd \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t trung phong \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung t\u1eeb Higuain l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/higuain-dong-y-toi-milan-176-192414.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan</span>, HLV Gatusso c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f2n Leonardo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong m\u1eaft ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Scaroni.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Alvaro Morata</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1edbi t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata co them co hoi khang dinh minh o Chelsea\" title=\"Morata c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/morata.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMorata mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Chelsea, song HLV Sarri d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea9y anh ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 Gonzalo Higuain.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Higuain, song l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Juventus nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n AC Milan, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 The Blues mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Higuain, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Sarri s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Morata \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Leonardo Bonucci</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leonardo Bonucci c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Milan \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2017 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro, v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 50 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bonucci tro lai Juventus chi sau mot mua giai ra di\" title=\"Bonucci tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ra \u0111i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/bonucci.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bonucci tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Bonucci kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap AC Milan gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6 \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Bonucci s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Gonzalo Higuain. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau 1 n\u0103m ra \u0111i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 l\u1ea1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Rugani s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Chelsea c\u00f2n Giorgio Chiellini v\u00e0 Andrea Barzagli \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i, Bonucci ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: HLV Maurizio Sarri</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf Napoli, \u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri khong the tai hop voi Higuain o Chelsea\" title=\"HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Higuain \u1edf Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/juve-mua-bonucci-milan-muon-higuain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Higuain \u1edf Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 Morata v\u00e0 Olivier Giroud \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. The Blues ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Higuain tr\u01b0\u1edbc AC Milan, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u00e0o tay c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&nbsp;th\u00e0nh Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Higuain, HLV Sarri s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Morata v\u00e0 Giroud. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Higuain v\u00e0 c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam Eden Hazard ho\u1eb7c Willian trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Cristiano Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gonzalo Higuain v\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nhau \u1edf Real Madrid, trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nhau 80 l\u1ea7n, ghi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 250 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo khong the choi ben canh Higuain mot lan nua\" title=\"Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Higuain m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Higuain m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHiguain v\u00e0 Ronaldo k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi nhau trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u1edf Bernabeu, NHM Juventus hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n CR7 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus, Ronaldo c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Higuain \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Juventus, anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Milan, Higuain s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Serie A v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Nicola Kalinic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nicola Kalinic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda \u1edf World Cup 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00ec l\u00fd do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0ng, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb HLV Zlatko Dalic t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nicola Kalinic nhieu kha nang se ngoi du bi cho Higuain\" title=\"Nicola Kalinic nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Higuain\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/kalinic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nicola Kalinic nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCroatia sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 song Nicola Kalinic th\u00ec m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1eaft NHM. M\u00f9a H\u00e8 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu Higuain c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Nicola Kalinic ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 31 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A, ch\u00ednh th\u00e0nh t\u00edch khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn AC Milan kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y Nicola Kalinic l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n* Squawka</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1909","checkdouble":"192568"},{"date":"17:42 02/08","title":"G\u00f3c Arsenal: Ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng l\u00e0n gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/2/goc-arsenal-niem-tin-tu-nhung-lan-gio-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>5 ch\u1eef k\u00fd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Unai Emery \u0111em v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u1edbn trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Arsenal. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Arsenal ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch mua</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Arsene Wenger, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 quen v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c &ldquo;Gi\u00e1o s\u01b0&rdquo; mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng. C\u00f3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 3 t\u00e2n binh trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, sau khi b\u00e1n Robin Van Persie cho k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Man United. Trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111em v\u1ec1 2 t\u00e2n binh (Lacazette, Kolasinac) t\u1eeb s\u1edbm, r\u1ed3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Unai Emery, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng quen v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng, \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n ng\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsene Wenger x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-mua-sokratis-wenger-phan-ngon-emery-phan-goc-172-191743.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/sokratis-noi-ve-arsenal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-mua-sokratis-wenger-phan-ngon-emery-phan-goc-172-191743.html\">Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Sokratis: Wenger t\u1eb7ng l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea7n ng\u1ecdn, Emery d\u1ef1ng x\u00e2y ph\u1ea7n g\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nArsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis t\u1eeb Dortmund v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 ti\u1ebfn tr\u00ecnh m\u1edf m\u00e0n tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n5 t\u00e2n binh gi\u00e0 c\u00f3, tr\u1ebb c\u00f3, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho CLB b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau. V\u00e0 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y khi Premier League chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u1edfi tranh, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 khung, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Wenger.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm, gi\u00fap Arsenal c\u00f3 th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch v\u00e0 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. M\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn C\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Arsenal ti\u1ebfn xa m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn C\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Arsenal ti\u1ebfn xa m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Goc-nhin-Cac-tan-binh-se-giup-Arsenal-tien-xa-mua-giai-sau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>3/5 t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Arsenal m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>&hellip;cho \u0111\u1ebfn vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh \u0111em v\u1ec1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eadn ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. \u00d4ng s\u1ebd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, v\u00e0 d\u1eb9p s\u1ef1 c\u00e1ch t\u00e2n m\u00e0 Wenger s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i l\u00e0 3-4-2-1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 c\u0169, Hector Bellerin s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, khi anh b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean qu\u00e1 cao trong vai tr\u00f2 wingback. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Unai Emery c\u00f2n \u0111em v\u1ec1 Stephan Lichtsteiner \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay th\u1ebf Bellerin khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, ho\u1eb7c trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u1edf m\u00f9a sau.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bellerin Lichtsteiner\" title=\"Bellerin Lichtsteiner\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/a1.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lichtsteiner c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 thay th\u1ebf Bellerin&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00e1i t\u00ean r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i Sokratis Papastathopoulos s\u1ebd \u0111i th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7, \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Mustafi. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Chambers, Holding hay Mavropanos s\u1ebd h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e0n anh, v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Arsenal khi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu s\u1ee9c \u00e9p ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khung g\u1ed7, Bernd Leno \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Petr Cech &ndash; th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh v\u1eeba &ldquo;t\u1ef1 \u00e1i&rdquo; v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ec9nh cao trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Chelsea. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o cho \u0111\u00e0n em, r\u1eb1ng: <strong>&ldquo;T\u1ea1i Premier League, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u1edf Anh.&rdquo;</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Morata \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Arsenal gi\u1eef v\u1eefng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, qua \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Chelsea c\u0169ng trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang. V\u00e0 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Cech \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Loftus-Cheek, gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Emery \u0111em v\u1ec1 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb l\u00e0 Torreira v\u00e0 Guendouzi, \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u00e9o b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Uruguay &ndash; Lucas Torreira ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 Xhaka v\u00e0 Ramsey r\u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal Emery\" title=\"Arsenal Emery\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/emery.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Emery c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Arsenal ti\u1ebfn xa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 Emery \u0111em v\u1ec1 s\u1ebd t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1ed1n c\u00f3. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho Arsenal khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chia s\u1ebb vai tr\u00f2 v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Emery l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n gi\u1ed1ng c\u00e1ch chia s\u1ebb quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c m\u00e0 Didier Deschamps \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i (<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhin-lai-thanh-cong-cua-tuyen-phap-mau-chot-la-su-doan-ket-421-191524.html\" target=\"_blank\">Les Bleus s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ebfn 6 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</span>). \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi, nh\u1eb1m \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam vi\u1ec7c v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Arsenal ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng ai \u0111\u1eb7t \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-chien-thang-cua-arsenal-truoc-chelsea-172-192524.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/nhung-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-chien-thang-cua-arsenal-truoc-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-chien-thang-cua-arsenal-truoc-chelsea-172-192524.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1i nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</span><br>\r\nG\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, Arsenal k\u1ebft th\u00fac chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u1edf m\u00e0n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-arsenal-11-pen-65-chelsea-icc-2018-326-192505.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/video-tong-hop-arsenal-11-pen-65-chelsea-icc-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-arsenal-11-pen-65-chelsea-icc-2018-326-192505.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Arsenal 1-1 (pen 6-5) Chelsea (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u00cdt nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 song Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-4-cai-ten-can-chung-to-minh-tai-arsenal-ngay-luc-nay-172-192082.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/goc-nhin-4-cai-ten-can-chung-to-minh-tai-arsenal-ngay-luc-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-4-cai-ten-can-chung-to-minh-tai-arsenal-ngay-luc-nay-172-192082.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Arsenal ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y</span><br>\r\nSau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Arsene Wenger, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ea7n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Unai...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1908","checkdouble":"192569"},{"date":"09:56 02/08","title":"\u0110T Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018, \u0110T Olympic Oman \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Oman t\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam chi\u1ec1u 1/8</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 1/8, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Oman \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 \u0111\u1ebfn 7/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n bay N\u1ed9i B\u00e0i, \u00f4ng Said Othman Al Balushi - T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd L\u0110B\u0110 Oman \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft, sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 Oman ch\u1ec9 th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Olympic Tokyo 2020.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 Oman c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Oman h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7. V\u00e0 trong th\u1eddi gian qua, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Azani \u0111\u00e3 thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Oman hi v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 Gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Olympic Oman ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 hai l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y \u00c1 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 0-6 v\u00e0 0-2. L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, Oman ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, song n\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\">U23 Uzbekistan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i ngay khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad-168-192521.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad-168-192521.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam luy\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi cho ASIAD</span><br />\r\nSau nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang trang b\u1ecb th\u00eam nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1907","checkdouble":"192528"},{"date":"10:38 02/08","title":"Nh\u1edd John Terry, Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/nho-john-terry-chelsea-sap-co-jack-grealish.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, nh\u1edd huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i John Terry \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eafp s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Jack Grealish</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Jack Grealish l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng, ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Chelsea-muon-co-Jack-Grealish-voi-gia-20-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jack Grealish \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ghi 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Aston Villa l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish-172-190672.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish</span>, Tottenham v\u00e0 M.U c\u0169ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Jack Grealish \u0111ang b\u1ecb dao \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Aston Villa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Villa Park \u0111\u00f2i 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Aston Villa s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 TTCN \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111ang \u0111i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Aston Villa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1eafp s\u1edf h\u1eefu Jack Grealish</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, nh\u1edd huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i John Terry \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eafp s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea sap co Jack Grealish\" title=\"Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jack Grealish\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/nho-john-terry-chelsea-sap-co-jack-grealish.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jack Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Blues m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u00ec ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp b\u1edfi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i John Terry \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Aston Villa nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i cho The Blues.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Terry \u0111\u00e1 cho Villa theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, anh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Villa Park. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1980 \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Villa b\u00e1n Grealish cho Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea m\u1edbi c\u00f3 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, HLV Sarri \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu The Blues th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u1ee5 Grealish, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1906","checkdouble":"192529"},{"date":"10:54 02/08","title":"Sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Chelsea c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/sao-tuyen-duc-chi-ra-van-de-chelsea-can-khac-phuc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u 1/8 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay ASIAD.</h2><h2>Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb PVF t\u1ea1i H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean, chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 1/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 \u0111\u1ebfn 7/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Lo-dien-cai-ten-thu-hai-se-phai-chia-tay-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo\u00a0chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 trong tay 28 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0nh l\u1eb7n, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1eadt c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n. Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua, Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i cho th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 m\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tr\u01a1n tru b\u00e0i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea7u bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lo ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy v\u00e0 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp ri\u00eang v\u1edbi gi\u00e1o \u00e1n ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c Choi Joo Yong, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho danh th\u1ee7 Park Ji Sung, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL Tu\u1ea5n Anh.. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u00e1ch c\u01a1. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ph\u00e9p ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo sau H\u1ed3ng Duy ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay ASIAD 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u00f3ng v\u1ea5n b\u00e1o ch\u00ed m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng Park th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 lo l\u1eafng n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0o n\u1eefa sau gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1t qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 7/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 11 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018-168-192528.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-oman-quyet-gay-bat-ngo-o-giai-tu-hung-2018-168-192528.html\">\u0110T Olympic Oman quy\u1ebft t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018, \u0110T Olympic Oman \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar-292-192527.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar-292-192527.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 \u00fd tr\u1ed1n \u0111i bar</span><br>\r\nNh\u00f3m 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 \u00fd tr\u1ed1n \u0111i bar nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Nepal khi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\">U23 Uzbekistan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i ngay khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1905","checkdouble":"192530"},{"date":"10:58 02/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Arsenal mu\u1ed1n Klopp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/20/huyen-thoai-arsenal-muon-klopp-ky-hop-dong-voi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Arsenal mu\u1ed1n HLV Klopp \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nabil Fekir c\u1ee7a Lyon trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nabil Fekir t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nabil Fekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t Ligue 1 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Lyon. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ghi 18 b\u00e0n \u1edf Ligue 1 v\u00e0 24 b\u00e0n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/Robert-Pires-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-vu-Nabil-Fekir-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool t\u1eebng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Liverpool. HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, \u00f4ng th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 t\u1edbi Anfield.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Lyon nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Liverpool ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro. Khi qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd, kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThe Kop sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Xherdan Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke City. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p n\u1eefa. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chanh-noi-khong-voi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-172-191696.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Fekir </span>khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lyon m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Robert Pires v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Arsenal mu\u1ed1n HLV Klopp \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nabil Fekir c\u1ee7a Lyon trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/25/Robert-Pires-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-vu-Nabil-Fekir-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robert Pires v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua\u00a0</span>Nabil Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cFekir l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho Liverrpool, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u1ea1i sao qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Liverpool\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc n\u1ebfu Liverpool b\u1ecf qua c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. C\u00f3 Nabil Fekir, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Fabinho, Naby Keita, Alisson v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1904","checkdouble":"192531"},{"date":"10:32 02/08","title":"\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 Tottenham nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/de-son-heungmin-du-asiad-2018-ldbd-han-quoc-nhuong-bo-nhung-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng v\u1edbi Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018 khi \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Son Heung-min ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. L\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 \"tr\u1ed1n\" ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1 b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, Son Heung-min v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n \u0111i l\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/De-Son-Heung-min-du-ASIAD-2018,-LDBD-Han-Quoc-nhuong-bo-nhung-gi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Son Heung-Min ph\u1ea3i xin ph\u00e9p Tottenham m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng chi\u1ebfn tranh n\u00ean m\u1ecdi c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n nam b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tham gia ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1. C\u00e1c v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean nam n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i Olympic ho\u1eb7c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ASIAD s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ASIAD 2018 kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a FIFA n\u00ean CLB Tottenham c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng cho Son Heung-min tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n khi ASIAD 2018 di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Premier League 2018-19 kh\u1edfi tranh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i Tottenham v\u00ec tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u0169ng th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Son Heung-min khi h\u1ecd c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ea1t ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 Son Heung-min tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Tottenham nh\u1eb1m \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t. Tottenham ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 Son Heung-min d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u hai tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Newcastle v\u00e0 Fullham.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung Min them mot lan nua bo lo co hoi ghi ban. Anh: \u200bFIFA.\" title=\"Son Heung Min th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa b\u1edf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n. \u1ea2nh: \u200bFIFA.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/de-son-heungmin-du-asiad-2018-ldbd-han-quoc-nhuong-bo-nhung-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Son Heung Min d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 nh\u1eb1m tr\u00e1nh ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn Fullham, Son Heung-min \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cho \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 1/9. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 xong v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f9 l\u1ea1i, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp Son Heung-min trong hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11/2018. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Son Heung-min c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 hai tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i VCK ASIAN Cup 2019 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i C\u00e1c ti\u1ec3u v\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u1ed1c \u1ea2-r\u1eadp Th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t (UAE).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang n\u1eb1m t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Kyrgyzstan, Malaysia, Bahrain v\u00e0 UAE.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-dien-cai-ten-thu-hai-se-phai-chia-tay-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-192533.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-nepal-phat-5-cau-thu-vi-di-bar-292-192527.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 \u00fd tr\u1ed1n \u0111i bar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-luyen-chien-thuat-moi-cho-asiad-168-192521.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam luy\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi cho ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-iraq-rut-lui-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad-18-co-the-phai-boc-tham-lai-168-192516.html\">Olympic Iraq r\u00fat lui, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 18 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vtv-bi-ep-gia-ban-quyen-asiad-tha-dau-mot-lan-roi-thoi-168-192504.html\">VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD: Th\u00e0 \u0111au m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i th\u00f4i!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-them-bat-loi-truoc-them-asiad-2018-168-192501.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn th\u00eam b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1903","checkdouble":"192532"}]}